      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以流程是：Education_StudentDB收到新连接→wait→proxied。wait有两个出口：超时10秒到disconnected，或者收到认证消息到proxied。对吗？",
